finished, and
all they have gained is the
shade of a tree.

24:54.793 --> 25:00.199 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Everyone is hungry, the old
woman tells me,
but better here than at home.

25:00.232 --> 25:06.572 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): The
soldiers came,
and so many people were killed,
even the women

25:06.605 --> 25:08.140 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and old people.

25:08.173 --> 25:10.809 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
My children were shot in front
of me.

25:10.843 --> 25:14.179 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The houses were burnt, so we ran
to the bush.

25:14.213 --> 25:18.851 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN RAY: There is food, but
nothing like
enough.

25:18.884 --> 25:23.756 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
