collect their
rations, but thousands have
arrived too late.

25:32.331 --> 25:37.302 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We found this woman picking
through the dirt
for a few grains split from the
sacks of cereal.

25:37.336 --> 25:41.006 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
In the long grass all around,
there are many
like her.

25:41.039 --> 25:43.308 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
