are water lilies.

26:06.799 --> 26:11.937 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM GAUL, South Sudan
(through translator):
I have never seen so many people
die of hunger.

26:11.970 --> 26:13.705 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Only God can help us now.

26:13.739 --> 26:17.409 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
