us will survive.

26:17.443 --> 26:23.182 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN RAY: This is Dalia, 6 years
old, perilously
thin.

26:23.215 --> 26:30.222 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
