front line
in a much wider struggle,
100,000 people on

26:30.255 --> 26:32.057 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the verge of starvation.

26:32.090 --> 26:37.563 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
