as her country,
uncertain fates intertwined.

26:37.596 --> 26:46.004 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, like so many children,
Khamis knows only
fear and hunger, first the war,
then the famine,

26:46.038 --> 26:50.175 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
now the reckoning.

