27:29.581 --> 27:33.719 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AL GORE, Former Vice President
of the United
States: My criticisms were not
mainly aimed

27:33.752 --> 27:41.426 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
at any individuals, including
President George
W. Bush or Vice President
Cheney, but rather

27:41.460 --> 27:49.434 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the way in which our democratic
conversation
has been degraded over the last
several decades.

27:49.468 --> 27:53.605 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I would say the same thing
about President
Trump.

27:53.639 --> 28:01.813 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For me, the most serious problem
is how our
nation became so vulnerable to
the assertion

28:01.847 --> 28:10.889 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
