the edge.

34:01.273 --> 34:08.013 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You're saying the
news media
can do its job and not be
accused on a regular

34:08.046 --> 34:11.216 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
basis of being fake news, as
this president
does?

34:11.249 --> 34:14.352 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AL GORE: Yes, fake news has been
around as
long as news has been around.

34:14.386 --> 34:19.591 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But, again, the issue is, how
vulnerable are
we to it?

34:19.624 --> 34:25.463 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
How can the immune system of
democracy, which
is not only the news media, but
also the free

34:25.497 --> 34:32.437 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
speech we all enjoy and the way
we make decisions
collectively, how can that
better protect

34:32.470 --> 34:36.808 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
us against blatant untruths that
are repeated
over and over again?

34:36.841 --> 34:39.611 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Are you
continuing to have
conversations with President
Trump?

34:39.644 --> 34:47.652 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AL GORE: Well, I'm not talking
about any dialogue
with him, direct or indirect.

34:47.686 --> 34:52.123 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I hope that our country remains
in the Paris
agreement.

34:52.157 --> 34:58.463 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But we face a climate crisis now
that is the
most serious challenge our
civilization has

34:58.496 --> 35:00.231 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
ever confronted.

35:00.265 --> 35:06.538 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the greatest country in the
world has
to remain a part of this
unprecedented global

35:06.571 --> 35:08.239 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
agreement to deal with it.

35:08.273 --> 35:10.041 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And you're
telling him that?

35:10.075 --> 35:13.845 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AL GORE: Well, again, I'm not
commenting on
my communications, because I
want to have

35:13.878 --> 35:15.547 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
more.

35:15.580 --> 35:17.449 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: All right, we
will leave it
there, former Vice President Al
Gore.

35:17.482 --> 35:22.354 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The book is "The Assault on
Reason," out with
a 10-years-later update.

35:22.387 --> 35:23.521 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
AL GORE: I thank you, Judy.

35:23.555 --> 35:31.396 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Thank you very
much.

