their methodology.

37:14.099 --> 37:15.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Exactly.

37:15.100 --> 37:16.901 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And that's what we want to do
right now.

37:16.935 --> 37:22.173 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We did just get, in the last few
hours, this
report, analysis, Amy, from the
Congressional

37:22.207 --> 37:23.975 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Budget Office.

37:24.008 --> 37:28.179 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Some good news interest for
Democrats, a little
bit of good news for the
administration.

37:28.213 --> 37:31.783 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMY WALTER: Well, if you're the
administration,
the first thing you look at, you
say, well,

37:31.816 --> 37:35.019 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
