is good news.

37:35.053 --> 37:41.092 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But at the core, Judy, this is
the challenge
for the Republican Party
fundamentally, which

37:41.126 --> 37:46.498 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
