States, who
is a Republican, went out on the
campaign

37:46.531 --> 37:50.668 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
trail and even when he was
president-elect
and said things like,
everybody's going to

37:50.702 --> 37:53.071 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
