for everybody.

37:53.104 --> 37:55.440 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He said that over and over
again.

37:55.473 --> 38:01.613 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the people in Congress and
those even
surrounding him, his HHS
secretary, the head

38:01.646 --> 38:06.384 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
